Details: Jamboree is the oldest institute in India and the best of its kind, which offers comprehensive classroom preparation programs for tests such as GMAT, GRE, SAT, TOEFLTM and IELTS. Jamboree centres are present in 14 cities of India and in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and Kathmandu . Each centre follows a uniform curriculum and has outstanding faculty, all of whom are trained in our head office. Each centre offers the same teaching standards and syllabus.At Jamboree, the most trusted name in India for education abroad, we help you give shape to your career and dreams. Founded in 1993, Jamboree attempted to fill the information gap on education abroad. Back then, the only information available on education abroad was through friends and family living or studying abroad. Thus, only a small percentage of interested students had access to information. Jamboree attempted to fill this information gap. Now when we in 'Team Jamboree' reflect on the past few years, we see thousands of our students on the thresholds of careers that would not have been possible without the right guidance at the right time.Jamboree, known for its thorough research and professionalism, is a one-stop shop for education abroad.Jamboree makes the entire process of studying abroad, from preparing to actually joining a foreign university, a smooth process. In recent years, the inclusion of several value-added services such as discounted couriers, educational loans and pre-departure orientation has made Jamboree Education Pvt. Ltd. a one-stop solution centre for all your study abroad requirements.

reviews:
I am lucky to be part of Prosper. They are reliable and very transparent in terms of process. I have received 4 I-20's out of 5 universities and happy to place myself in one of the best university which I aspired of.

Prosper updated me the status of my application in a timely manner and communicated with me all through the proceedings. It is because of their assistance I was able to secure admission.

Before visiting prosper I have visited few consultants but did not find the assistance which I expected. I found them to be very good in all streams and without thinking for a minute I enrolled with them

Really love the way they deal with students,I want to thank prosper overseas. They have made my dream come true. During my first visit based on my profile they suggested me good university. Then the admin department guided me with the list of documents to be submitted and explained me the entire application process and they even gave me the software details where I could track the status of my applications.

I just visited them 4-5 times for submitting my documents after that I used to get emails and notifications in software for my status updates.
       The processing department completed my application on time and everything was transparent. I was updated on my status timely.

I am very happy I got admit from University of Manitoba, the visa department assisted me with the visa process they guided me very well with the visa requirements, documents checklist and assisted me with filling the visa applications.

With their assistance I submitted my visa application to Canada high commissions and after 3 weeks I got good news that MY VISA IS APPROVED for fall 2016.

I always received good response from everyone whenever I needed.
My classes are going to commence from September 6 th and I have booked my flight ticket and even interacted with the university regarding my orientation.

I never thought that I will be flying to Canada, I visited many consultancies but none of them guided me well the way prosper overseas did.

Few consultants even said my profile is not suitable but prosper overseas suggested me with the right university based on my profile.
I must even conclude that the service and processing fees are very affordable comparatively with other consultants.

The staff was very polite and professional and they all gave me very good services.

I will suggest all my friends and relatives to opt prosper oversea services since they have individual departments throughout the processing stage.

Thank you prospers overseas once again for such a good experience.,The best thing about this consultancy is that they have portal for students which provide various access to the students in term of getting updates.

With the help of this facility I could check all my updates; I did not have to visit my consultant personally for submitting the documents as I had the feasibility of   uploading it directly. I directly used to communicate with my consultant with the help of this portal facility.

I registered with Prosper Overseas for my USA process and processed my application for admission to 5 universities.

Throughout my processing this consultancy has helped me with booking for GRE and TOFEL slot, WES evaluation and score reporting to the universities.
I am the first person in my family who is planning for abroad education and I had no proper knowledge on the application process but after visiting them, consultancy really gave me an excellent informative session on the procedure of the applications.

All I knew about was GRE & TOFEL, but they even explained me about the various credentials evaluations which increase the chances of admit in desired universities.

The admin department helped me with the sample copies of documents and statement of purpose, application fees, score reporting etc.
Prosper overseas processing department filled all the applications in front of me to ensure that the application is error free.

I have received admits from 3 universities, 2 is under process.

I have decided to attend my visa interview with university of maryland baltimore county  as it is my  desired university.

Currently prosper overseas is guiding me with the visa process. They have given me counseling on filling up DS-160 Form, Booking my visa slot and even guided me with the documents which I need to produce during my interview with the consulate.

They are even conducting mock interviews which are boosting my confidence level and I am sure I will be able to excel in my interview.
I did not face obstacle during my application process as I was getting my updates on time and the admissions department was always available to solve my doubts.

I am expecting to receive such services till the time I depart to USA.,Excellency is the key word 

I really appreciate the  process and  the procedure that Prosper Overseas follow. Take it dealing with the selection of the universities or dealing with the queries that usually student have during the procedure, they are experts I must say.

They are so very clear with the selection and the shortlisting of the universities that all the universities I applied to accepted my profile. This is so very good. In the initial few days of application itself I secured acceptance with one university and gradually with other universities. 

I really must tell you that they are super fast in expediting the things to the university and then to the student. All the document asked by the university where delivered on time. On every step of the process they assist with  their best team.

Even the submissions of my application were done in a very scrutinized way. They did send the applications for my review so that I may also check my applications.

FLOCKS please visit this consultancy, they will make you aw stuck with their service.

Thanks for all the good work Prosper Overseas,Great news guys..!!!

With the limited technological resources available at the time, Prof Rane started correspondence training courses for various management entrance examinations to Indian business schools, and was the ambassador for the MBA degree and its opportunities in India. Instead of the MBA being an obscure, little-heard of field of study in India, IMS turned it into a dream education for the majority.

reviews:
I would like to share my experience with Can Consultants, Ahmedabad.

When I started searching for various consultancy firms for Canada PR, I came to know about Can Consultants with the help of internet. Before registering at Can Consultants I made inquiries at various consultancy firms at Ahmedabad viz. Y-Axis, GEPSI, NB International etc...

The reason why I chose Can Consultants is that they are more transparent than any other consultants at Ahmedabad. Out of 5 to 6 consultants I met before registering to Can Consultants, two of them literally told me that I won't get PR and so I should go for student visa. In this way other consultants were insisting me to register for student visa. When I met one of the staff members at Can consultants for the first time, they told me straight forward that I could get PR and there is no need to go for student visa.

During my entire process of Canada PR the staff and Mr. Pankaj Patel have been very helpful and transparent throughout the process. The guidance provided by Can Consultants helped me get PR within 9 months of period.

I would like to mention also that apart from process of PR, Can consultants helped me in IELTS coaching, currency conversion, and post landing services in a sincere way which I think any other consultancy firm would not provide at this best.

As far as the consultancy fees is concerned, I would admit that Can Consultants are very much transparent with no hidden cost. Also they charge very reasonable fees as compared to other firms.

In short, I would say that above are the reasons why I suggest anyone to register with the Can Consultants and why Can Consultants are best in the industry.

Thanks a lot to all the staff members at Can Consultants & Mr. Pankaj Patel help me achieve my dreams.,I have registered with CAN consultants to process my "Application for Points Based Skilled Migration Visa" for Australia. Mr. Pankaj Patel (owner) had arranged personal meeting with me before registration and first check my eligibility and provide full information regarding documentation, Competency Demonstration Report (CDR) and IELTS related to application.He had checked all three CDR and documents before applying for 'Skills  Assessment' to 'EngineersAustralia'. After getting positive 'Skills Assessment', he had arranged another personal meeting with me and provide information regarding documentation before applying for State Sponsorship. After getting successful State Sponsorship Letter, he had arranged another personal meeting with me and provide full information (including Medical, PCC and Physical Inquiry) before applying for Visa. During whole procedure Mr.Pankaj Patel and other faculty members have provided full support and taken a prompt action to solve all the queries raised.Due to of CAN Consultant's Transparency, Higher Accuracy and Precautions. I have got my VISA in just two months of my visa application. I had contacted many consultants in Surat, Baroda and Ahmedabad before processing my visa application, but I got success only by CAN Consultant. Their charges are lowest so far than other consultants.,,,

reviews: I have been taking GRE coaching under Jamboree. I would like to thank jamboree for all the support. Faculty here are very patient in clearing the doubts.Their expert advice helped me a lot in getting a good score. Jamboree's excellent study material and mock tests helped me succeed with good score. Thank you for everything.,I have been taking GMAT coaching from December 2015 from Jamboree. I recently gave my GMAT and scored 690. The class material is more than enough to practice and it is covers all the important things. The maths and verbal faculties have been very dynamic and energetic throughout. Each faculties give personal attention and critical feedback and help you to create study plan. They also have daily online webinars which are very helpful for solving tough questions.,I have been taking SAT coaching from January 2016 from jamboree institute . It has been a wonderful experience to have SAT coaching from Jamboree. The Maths faculty have large experience about abroad studies, teaches us the large number of tricks, they not only teach for the SAT but also help in selection of colleges . The class material provides lucid examples of how to go about answering questions in a logical way so that even if one encounters new words one can still make a shrewd guess. Also, the class size is optimum ensuring personal interaction.,A GMAT Score of 690 and a perfect quant score of Q-51, the credit goes to Jamboree (Ahmedabad). It had been a great place for the GMAT preparation and the journey throughout had been most pleasing, thanks to amazing and ever available faculties and admin staff. The personal attention, critical feedback,& easy access to faculties for doubt clearing sessions was exactly what I needed and was pleased to get it at Jamboree. The customized study plan  specific to my academic level, effective solutions/ ways to solve to Blue Book and constant assistance in quant helped me achieve Q-51. Apart from faculty, the administrative team too, was more than supporting , all along the process. I am grateful to Jamboree for my score. I sincerely endorse Jamboree to all GMAT aspirants out there, and am sure you will  feel the same experience as have I.,I have been taking SAT coaching from march 2016 from jamboree institute . The teaching experience was good. Quant faculty was very good in teaching and has a much of experience with a vast field of knowledge . The class material provides various examples of how to go about answering questions in a logical way so that even if one encounters new words one can still make a shrewd guess.Culture of the class was really good. The counselors are experienced about abroad studies and they have a lot on research on it.

Madhavi Mam is a excellent person & Best Tutor, she given 100% attention & effort to all student to achieve maximum BAND in IELTS & any abroad entrance exam so without any hesitation just join this class and definitely you will get max score.
All staff is very nice & supportive but specially Mr.Varshang Sir  is support is mind blowing.
Nice Classes, Library, Discussion room & Given Birthing to all student and also Weekly MOCK TEST taken for improvement.
One can get all the personal attention required from the tutors and the appropriate guidance required to crack an exam and come out with flying colors. 
I am personally thankful for the constant support provided as well as of elevating my confidence with the positive approach of the faculties.
Thank You Varshang Sir & Madhvi Mam for support in IELTS preparation.,Anyone want to register from ‪#‎British‬ ‪#‎Academy‬ then contact me. I have one interesting news for them and i have special review regarding ‪#‎madhavikhandwala‬.

This is very wellknow guidance and informative.Teaching methods and techniques are extremely appropriate and practical.,It was great time spend at British academy for learning & upgrading self in international language.
Faculty members are 100% devoted themselves to improve individual in all 4 pillars of IELTS.
Library facilities, flexible timing, tips/tricks/techniques,  enough practice time leads me to crack my exam in first go with desired band.  HIGHLY RECOMMENDED.,Its grate experience to learn from madhavi Ma'am they are providing best coaching in ielts and pte

reviews:
Great Market.. Mainly famous for Bar and Resturants with good and tastey foods. You can have good time in evening. Necessary shops are available.  Good Crowd.. Little costly however worth as per locality and market,Very posh & happening cosy market at one corner u will find pocket friendly Burgers , kebabs , wine , bakery at opposite lane all good restaurants my personal favorite is Sagar for SouthIndia food & Swagat for nice gala dinner ... This serves everything from Indian , Chinese to continental.
There are so many Flowers shop with all sort of rare/ imported fresh fregrent flowers
Lots of Paan shops there at ever corners.
Cool place to hang out .,Has everything. Slightly upscale atmosphere. Wide range of good restaurants. A few stores. Home services. Superb location. Fully functional circular market. Top eating out options. Slightly chaotic but accessible car parking. Even a liquor vend and more than one bar. Easy on families until 9pm.,Check out Kakori Kabab along with Roomali roti + Beer.... Amazing,Nice place to hang out. Try kulfi or have your food at Swagat... you'll love it.

reviews:
A wonderful place. Unusual decoration and atmosphere for the city of Ahmedabad.
Food is quite good, ambience is pleasant, and you can buy everything that is in the cafe, from the chair you are seated on to the lamps or design objects you can find displayed.
A variety of food, snacks and drinks. 
Definitely a place to go, while in the city!,The place has an extremely creative bent and is super cool... The ambience  is really cool n' Coz of its chilled out attitude, it's a perfect place to keep
Visiting...

Food wise, The cold coffee is awesome, wood fired pizza is pretty good with a good amount of cheese...
Tried the waffles and they are pretty neat... The chestnuts in plum sauce are a pleasant change... 

Overall the food quality is super and it's always a pleasure to come back to the place with efficient service... 

The lady who owns the place is super friendly and makes sure that thins are all under control and well managed... 

Cheers to the people👍🏻👍🏻
,'The Project Cafe' A name with a hint of something creative in it. Ambiance was perfectly pleasant (more in case of a date 😉). It was different, something new for a café.

Interiors were cool, and everything here was on sale too. One of the posters said that they were even listed on 'The Vogue' , which is great.

Food Part : We ordered 'Mexican Chilli Paneer Rice' , a 'Double Shot Cold Coffee' and a 'Mint Mojito'. The Mexican rice was good. Tasted great but nothing extraordinary. Coffee was good too, at first didn't feel like 'double shot', but after proper mixing of coffee on the top, it's taste grew stronger, but again nothing extraordinary.

Overall, a very nice place to come and spend some quality time with friends, or it being only you.

P.S : Cafe is good and all, but some of the preparations are over priced.
,Good food but lousy interiors ,This cafe is something different from the usual coffee shops. Strategically placed merchandise can have visitors eye everywhere. The food quality is just about okay. A one time visit place if you are hungry for some change..

reviews:
A CONTINUOUS FLOW OF CONGRATULATIONS FOR YOUR PLAYING REAL ROLE AS SARTHI  FOR THE SUCCESS OF STUDENTS & THE NEW WEBSITE AND PUBLICATION OF 'SARTHI' 

Your road was tough, but you did an excellent job. You never lost your faith and courage, which eventually brought you to success. Congratulations.

Your character, composure, focus and courage, has earned you this success and glory and let the spirit never fade away. Congratulations 

Congratulations!  Keep aiming higher! The sky is the limit!
I am so happy that you made yourself and your parents proud. Keep it up. Congratulations!

With this new glory, shall come more challenges and obstacles in life ahead. Face them with same courage and determination, and success will keep flowing in. Heartiest congratulations to you. 

It is a success, you truly deserved. It is an achievement you have truly earned. I congratulate you on your success and wish you all the best for your future. Well done.
With enthusiasm and hard work like yours, success was certain to be achieved. Well done. Congratulations on this wonderful achievement. 
It is a success, you truly deserved. It is an achievement you have truly earned. I congratulate you on your success and wish you all the best for your future. Well done.
Some are dreamers, some are talented. You are both. May you achieve more success ahead. Congratulations on this success. 
Congratulations on having the same great idea as someone who successfully executed it.
You are always keeping in mind and putting in action in your life those are the following......

It's so simple to be happy, but so difficult to be simple.

Wisdom is not a product of schooling, but of the life- long attempt to acquire it. 

We are here to add what we can to life, not to get what we can from life. You are first one !

The believer is happy, the doubter is wise. You are first one !

Life doesn't require that we be the best, only that we try our best. You are trying your best!

One of the secrets of a long and fruitful life is to forgive everybody everything every night before you go to bed. ...that you do every night!

I lived what most people call the good life. I was happy, but deep inside I always felt that, with the short amount of time we are given to live and love in this world, we spend too much time loving things instead of people. You spend too much time for people not for things!

If in our daily life we can smile, if we can be peaceful and happy, not only we, but everyone will profit from it. This is the most basic kind of peace work. This thing you have done my brother!

To be healthy, wealthy, happy and successful in any and all areas of your life you need to be aware that you need to think healthy, wealthy, happy and successful thoughts twenty four hours a day and cancel all negative, destructive, fearful and unhappy thoughts. These two types of thought cannot coexist if you want to share in the abundance that surrounds us all. You are trying to have positive thoughts ever!

reviews:
It was a very good experience for me.
I strongly recommended this institute to everyone who want to speak English fluently.
There is a problem in our teaching method so we have a fear or difficulty in speaking English. But here sir teach us English grammar and extraordinary methods very easily and friendly so we can easily come out from our fear of speaking English and get confidence to speak english fluently. My personal experience is that now I can speak English easily and confidently.
All the staff of turning point is very helpful and always ready to support the students in their weak areas of speaking English.
Every one has to join this institute to know English perfectly and easily.,Before joining turning point institute my english  is not good . After  I joined that my english grammar is well,  overcome my stage fear & also speaking english very well before joining TP. Ashish sir and Pragna mam are very helpful person and  co-operate  with us. They have also help for  preparing of  Interview and Project. Join this  TPI ....... I love TP.................!!!!!!!!,It was a superb experience to learn English here . The sir and all faculty members are too good and supportive.
If u really want to learn a proper English just be here and u will definitely get the positive result. They create a motivation in the students to learn it and  the activities they keeps are really great . Through these activities we get confidence in ourself and motivation too.,First day I had come to TP then i had thought that it's very difficult to speak in english for me bcoz i m housewife nd i had left my study since 9yrs but after day by day sir taught only 4-5 rules in entire english then i realised that it's very easy to learn bcoz of ashish sir nd pragna mam. They both r fantastic nd their teaching system is fabulous. It was a nice jouney of 2 mounth.,I have survyed a lot before joining this institute, and i am glad that i took the decision of joining turning point, the reason i would like to tell you that the english is taught here is in the simplest way u can learn, u get to know that english is made up of only 3 to 4 rules..u ll be able to speak fluently within 2 months. The english which u have learnt in past and the fluency in which u r struggling will become so easy that you ll surprisd that in this way fluency can be get easily...so if you are searching for improving the english, your search ends here..
